    "causal_summary": "Per opencode official docs (`https://opencode.ai/docs/skills`, `/agents`, `/commands`), opencode's project-level discovery looks for **`.opencode/skills/`**, **`.opencode/agents/`**, **`.opencode/commands/`** (all plural). This repo uses singular for all three, so opencode's built-in discovery silently fails on every dispatch. This packet aligns the repo with opencode convention.",
